    <note>Sun(1) Danian [21418] Sichuan TZ, 122.33a (Shaosheng jinshi, year a guess). Same mingzi as the first mingzi of Zhaoyuan [21399], grandson of Bian [1540], which Zhaoyuan may have changed to avoid duplicating the mingzi of a cousin who remained in Sichuan. On the other hand, since Zhaoyuan is still listed as a Meizhou jinshi in Sichuan TZ even though his grandfather had moved to Zhengzhou, the Meishan Sun(1) with the generational name X+nian may all be grandsons of Bian. I make them all nephews of Zhaoyuan's father, Zhe [21439], but retain their Meishan address. Minwen [21403] has the same generational name as Zhaoyuan's sons, and I make a lineage (second) grandnephew of Zhe. Kinship based on address, generational name and chronological logic.</note>
